title: For Sale:  H&K USP .40
postcontent: Heckler & Koch USP full size, .40 caliber with 4-ten round, H&K factory magazines and 400-rounds of ammunition.  The pistol offered is a safe queen with a very low round count.  It is in like new condition and features a custom ghost ring rear sight and a rubber sleeve on the grip.  The USP was introduced in the late 80's and H&K designed it specifically for law enforcement and military use.  Later on down the line USSOCOM picked it up as well as other allied forces.  The USP stems from the model 1911 pistol, a popular and dependable design from the 20th century.  Where the USP differs is the polymer grip instead of metal, which makes it lighter in weight.  Shooters can pull the slide back to set the trigger for single action or choose to decock it with the safety and set it for double action on the first round fired.  It has an ambidextrous magazine release and safety.  On the front of the lower receiver is a universel rail for mounting a light or a laser.  This is an excellent quality, 100% reliable, accurate pistol.
